  "detailed_description": "Bare Metal is a fast-paced tug-of-war game. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nEach player has 4 towers that produce units: Tank, Chopper, Anti-Air and Mobile Bomb. Your base generates power to spend on units. Units get a veteran level for every three kills. You can spend more power to produce a veteran unit. Victory is achieved by killing your enemy’s units and towers.",
